===Noun===
{{en-noun2|'''vagina'''|'''[[vaginas]] '''or''' [[vaginae]]'''}}

#{{anatomy}} The passage leading from the opening of the [[vulva]] to the [[cervix]] of the [[uterus]] in [[female]] [[mammal]]s.
#A similar part in some invertebrates.
#{{botany}} A sheathlike structure, such as the leaf of a grass that surrounds a stem.

